---
import Button from "../components/button.astro";
import Projects from "../components/home/projects.astro";
import Separator from "../components/home/separator.astro";
import Writings from "../components/home/writings.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="RYL">
  <div
    class="relative z-20 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 px-7 md:mt-24 lg:mt-32 xl:px-0"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row">
      <div class="relative w-full md:w-1/2">
        <h1
          class="mb-5 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white"
        >
          Hi! I'm Richard.
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
<br /><br />I have a solid foundation in programming across multiple languages, including C++, Python, HTML/CSS, and JavaScript, as well as interpretive languages such as Markdown and LaTeX. I participated in FRC robotics training and led the mechanical design of five robots.

<br /><br />Aficionado of linguistics, politics, and history, I have conducted research projects on extinct East Asian languages, performed public policy analyses on East Asian geopolitics, and developed a history-oriented oral interview series. One research paper focusing on nationalism was published.

<br /><br />An active student leader, I have secured internships in high school admissions, outreach, and interviewing. I also conducted data research focused on predicting stock movements and gained insights in real-world stock trading.

<br /><br />As an avid athlete, I am a professional golf player who competes in state-level competitions. Additionally, I have extensive experience in badminton, table tennis, squash, and soccer. 
        </p>
        <Button text="Connect with me on LinkedIn" link="https://www.linkedin.com/in/richard-yliu/" />
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative justify-end hidden w-full mt-10 md:flex md:pl-10 md:w-1/2 md:mt-0 md:translate-y-4 xl:translate-y-0"
      >
        <div class="relative z-50 w-full">
          <div class="relative z-30 px-10">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/photo-min.png"
              loading="eager"
              decoding="auto"
              class="relative z-30 w-full aspect-[500/702] md:max-w-md mx-auto dark:-translate-y-0.5"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 z-20 w-full h-full lg:h-[420px] translate-x-0 -translate-y-px border border-dashed rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r dark:from-neutral-950 dark:via-black dark:to-neutral-950 from-white via-neutral-50 to-white border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
